import {
  Box,
  Text,
  VStack,
  Input,
  Flex,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  Button,
  Heading,
  FormErrorMessage,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

export const InputDiv = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box w="100%">
        <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs" htmlFor="email">
          Email
        </FormLabel>
      </Box>
      <Input
        placeholder="Digite seu email"
        bg="#343B41"
        color="#F8F9FA"
        {...register("email")}
      />
      <FormErrorMessage>{errors.email?.message}</FormErrorMessage>
      <Box w="100%" mt="20px">
        <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs" htmlFor="password">
          Senha
        </FormLabel>
      </Box>
    </>
  );
};
